item.title: CVE-2017-5242|2024-08-05T14:55:35.797Z -- rapid7 -- nexpose%20virtual%20appliance
item.description: Nexpose and InsightVM virtual appliances downloaded between April 5th, 2017 and May 3rd, 2017 contain identical SSH host keys. Normally, a unique SSH host key should be generated the first time a virtual appliance boots.
